    <text type="letter">
        <body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><p><seg rend="left"><pb facs="DSC_0641.JPG"/><hi rend="pre-print">D<hi rend="superscript">r.</hi> Max Burckhard</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><del rend="strikethrough">Wien, IX. Porzellangasse 48</del><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#dots" n="10"/></hi></seg></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#33" type="place">St. Gilgen</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>12. 9. 1911</date></p><salute>Liebſter verehrter Herr Doctor!</salute></opener><p>Erlauben Sie, daſs ich Ihnen und der verehrten Frau <rs type="person" ref="#2173" subtype="implied">Gemahlin</rs> mein aufrichtigſtes <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL967-1"/><rs type="person" ref="#12701" subtype="implied">Beileid</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL967-1h">Zum Tod von <rs ref="#2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs>s Mutter <rs ref="#12701" type="person">Louise</rs> am <date>9. 9. 1911</date>.</note> zu dem bitteren Verluſte, den Sie erlitten, ausſpreche.</p><closer>In Treue Ihr<lb/><signed>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Burckhard</signed></closer></div></body>
